title: Britney Spears teases fans with three sultry bikini videos
text:
Britney Spears teases fans with three sultry bikini videos

CLOSE

Alert, alert, alert! Britney Spears is back!

Not like she ever left, but you know she has a flair for the dramatic — so much so that the pop princess quietly debuted three videos on her Instagram on Monday.

In the caption-less black-and-white videos, Spears showcases her abs, stares seductively into the camera and whips her platinum blonde tresses around like her life depended on it while clad in nothing but a black bikini and fake tattoos — and all while Nathaniel Rateliff & The Night Sweats' S.O.B. plays on.

While we appreciate good ole fashioned flexing just as much as the next person, we can't help but wonder what this means. Is this a teaser for the Piece for Me singer's show once her Las Vegas residency resumes? Or did she just stunt on us for no reason? Only time will tell. In the meantime, we'll just be over here, picking up the pieces of our lives.
